OL,3,CAutistic man who lost voluntary job at
OL,4,CWaitrose to return in paid role
OL,6,FAn autistic man who lost his voluntary
OL,7,Fjob at Waitrose is returning to the
OL,8,Fstore in a paid role.
OL,10,FTom Boyd, 28, had been working at a
OL,11,FWaitrose store in Cheadle Hulme,
OL,12,FCheshire, for four years, accompanied
OL,13,Fby a support worker.
OL,15,FWhen his mother asked the supermarket
OL,16,Fchain in July if he could be offered a
OL,17,Ffew paid hours the head office ended
OL,18,Fthe work placement.
