OL,3,CAutistic man who lost voluntary job at
OL,4,CWaitrose to return in paid role
OL,6,FAfter his story made the headlines and
OL,7,Fhe was offered a job at Asda, Waitrose
OL,8,Foffered him his job back with pay.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday 9 December, the firm
OL,11,Fconfirmed he would be returning to
OL,12,Fwork in January, after the Christmas
OL,13,Frush.
OL,15,FA Waitrose spokesman said: "We're
OL,16,Fdelighted that Tom has accepted our
OL,17,Foffer of paid employment and looking
OL,18,Fforward to welcoming him to start in
OL,19,FJanuary, as requested by his family.
