OL,6,F"We have Tom's best interests at heart
OL,7,Fand we've worked closely with his
OL,8,Ffamily throughout to ensure Tom gets
OL,9,Fthe support he needs.
OL,11,F"We're learning from this situation
OL,12,Fand working with charities and
OL,13,Fspecialists to make sure we can
OL,14,Fcontinue to offer fair and rewarding
OL,15,Fopportunities for people with
OL,16,Fneurodiversity."
